column2: SELECT   a.specObjID, a.plateid, a.mjd,   a.targettype, a.z, a.ra, a.dec, a.spectrotype,   b.modelFlux_z, b.psfFlux_z, b.fiberFlux_z, b.psfFlux_z,   b.modelMag_z, b.psfMag_z, b.fiberMag_z, b.petroMag_z   b.cModelMag_z into mydb.phototable1 FROM galSpecInfo AS a   JOIN PhotoObjAll AS b      ON a.specObjID = b.specObjID
